    <p class="section-number">02, SKS repair categories</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Refrigeration columns, Pro ranges, dishwashers, cooktops, wall ovens.</h2>

    <div class="callout-box">
      <h3>2018-2022 SKS column fridge ice maker + InstaView panel pattern (most common SKS service call in LA)</h3>
      <p>The integrated column refrigerators manufactured between roughly 2018 and 2022 — SKSCJ3606S and similar 36-inch variants — develop a matched-cycle pattern around year 3 to 4 where both the ice maker module and the InstaView panel connectivity fail within months of each other. The ice maker module shows up first about 60% of the time (intermittent ice production, then full stop), followed by InstaView panel issues (knock-detection stops working, or the interior lighting fails to trigger, or the panel display shows connectivity errors). Either symptom alone is a $285-$580 service item; the matched pattern means we typically diagnose both at the same visit and propose paired service to avoid a return trip in 3-6 months. Total paired service: $585-$985 with OEM SKS / LG parts, typically completed in 2 visits (diagnostic + parts arrival) with the LG-network 2-5 day lead.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="appliance-grid">
      <div class="appliance-card">
        <h3>Integrated column refrigerators</h3>
        <p>Full-height refrigerator columns, freezer columns, wine columns specified individually and installed side-by-side. Compressor, evaporator fan, condenser fan, defrost timer, ice maker module, InstaView panel, water filter system, control board service.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="appliance-card">
        <h3>Pro Dual-fuel ranges (with sous vide)</h3>
        <p>SKSDR480SS 48-inch and SKSDR360GS 36-inch Pro Dual-fuel ranges. Gas burner cooktop with integrated sous vide circulator zone, electric convection oven, integrated steam oven cavity. Burner igniters, sous vide circulator pump, steam oven water-fill system, oven thermostat, convection fan motor service.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="appliance-card">
        <h3>Induction cooktops</h3>
        <p>SKSCV30K and similar 30, 36-inch induction cooktops. Induction generator boards, cooktop glass replacement, induction coil service, control panel. Brand-specific induction electronics distinct from LG standard induction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="appliance-card">
        <h3>Built-in wall ovens</h3>
        <p>SKSCV2402S double oven, SKSCV3001P single 30-inch wall oven. Bake / broil element, convection fan motor, oven thermostat, control board, door hinge service. Smart-platform integration with LG ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="appliance-card">
        <h3>Dishwashers</h3>
        <p>SKSDW2402P standard tub and SKSDW2401P top-control variants. 24-inch panel-ready integrated dishwashers. Drain pump, water inlet valve, control board, door latch, spray arm assembly service.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="appliance-card">
        <h3>Range hoods</h3>
