        <h3>SKS SKSCJ3606S 36-inch column refrigerator, Hancock Park</h3>
        <p><strong>Symptom:</strong> Ice production intermittent for 2 weeks, then stopped completely. InstaView knock-detection started showing errors the same week. Unit was 4 years old, 2021 column-fridge cohort.</p>
        <p><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> Classic 2018-2022 SKS column-fridge matched-pattern failure — ice maker module fully failed plus InstaView control board firmware fault triggering connectivity errors. Compressor and other refrigeration components within spec.</p>
        <p><strong>Repair:</strong> Ice maker module replacement plus InstaView control board replacement, both with OEM SKS / LG parts (LG-network 3-day arrival). Verified ice production resumed within 12 hours and InstaView functioning normally.</p>
        <p><strong>Cost & time:</strong> $725 total. Two visits — diagnostic + parts arrival, 3 days apart.</p>
